<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink398">
<l>puḷḷu maṟiyāp palpaḻam paḻuṉi</l>
<l>maṭamā ṉaṟiyāt taṭanīr nilaiic</l>
<l>curanaṉi yiṉiya vākuka veṉṟu</l>
<l>niṉaittoṟuṅ kaliḻu meṉṉiṉu</l>
<l>mikapperitu pulampiṉṟu tōḻinam mūrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>“May the wilderness become very pleasant, </l>
<l>and may many fruits unknown even to birds grow ripe [there],  </l>
<l>and many large water reservoirs  </l>
<l>unknown even to delicate deers remain [there]!”,   </l>
<l>so I cried every time I thought [about you],  </l>
<l>but our village worried even more than I did, [my] friend! </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
